    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "You would need to edit the js to enable an in-place execution. `/frontend/html/notebook/static/js/notebook.js`. \n\n``` javascript\n    // control/apple E: execute (apple - E is easier than shift E)\n    if ((event.ctrlKey || event.metaKey) && event.keyCode==69) { \n      that.execute_selected_cell({addnew:false, select_next:false});\n      return true;\n    }\n```\n\nI have that in my branch to map apple+E to execute. \n"
